4
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:56,030
Bah.

5
00:00:56,230 --> 00:00:58,260
What an Ancestral Court of the Human Race.

6
00:00:58,260 --> 00:01:02,130
How dare they make a prospective emperor of our clan kneel to receive an edict.

7
00:01:02,130 --> 00:01:03,500
My woodcutter's knife

8
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:05,800
