9
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:07,430
Kill.

10
00:01:07,530 --> 00:01:09,900
Kill until the ocean flows for hundreds of millions of miles.

11
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:12,600
Slaughter millions of soldiers of the Ancestral Court.

12
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,160
What an Imperial Clan Gu Family.

13
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,200
What a Gu Linyuan.

14
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:17,620
How dare he smash my envoy into ashes.

15
00:01:18,100 --> 00:01:19,560
As Qingqing said,

16
00:01:20,230 --> 00:01:23,030
