17
00:01:23,030 --> 00:01:24,230
Once their wings are full,

18
00:01:24,230 --> 00:01:25,630
they will definitely have rebellious intentions.

19
00:01:25,630 --> 00:01:26,430
Your Majesty.

20
00:01:26,630 --> 00:01:28,930
That old devil Gu Linyuan killed the envoy.

21
00:01:28,930 --> 00:01:31,030
He didn't take the Ancestral Court seriously at all.

22
00:01:31,030 --> 00:01:33,200
The Gu family must have colluded with the Demons long ago,

23
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:35,800
so they dared to rescue the remaining evil blood of the Luo clan without authorization.

24
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,960
They are traitors to our entire human race.

25
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:39,600
Your Majesty, please give the order immediately.

26
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:41,729
Call upon the righteous armies of the world

27
00:01:41,729 --> 00:01:43,229
to attack the Gu family

28
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:46,100
to rectify the heavenly majesty of our human orthodox.

29
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:46,460
Good.

30
00:01:47,430 --> 00:01:49,860
I will issue the Imperial Edict of the Human Emperor.

31
00:01:49,860 --> 00:01:50,460
This time,

32
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,229
I will exterminate the nine generations of Gu Linyuan

33
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:56,090
and trample the Gu Family of the Eastern Wasteland.

34
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:11,430
Sons of the human race,

35
00:02:11,830 --> 00:02:14,200
it's time to pick up your weapons

36
00:02:14,330 --> 00:02:16,130
and fight for our human orthodox

37
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:17,160
