38
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,530
The Imperial Clan Gu Family

39
00:02:19,530 --> 00:02:20,600
colluded with the Demon Clan

40
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:21,800
and harbored the sinful blood.

41
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,730
They are indeed traitors of our human race for all eternity.

42
00:02:24,730 --> 00:02:26,329
All those of human bloodline

43
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:28,090
should be executed together.

44
00:02:39,930 --> 00:02:41,230
Jiang Yun, this idiot.

45
00:02:41,829 --> 00:02:42,630
The human race

46
00:02:42,829 --> 00:02:43,560
is finished.

47
00:02:50,329 --> 00:02:52,590
Luo Jinghong has left the Imperial Pass.

48
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:55,360
Now the Imperial Pass of the human race is leaderless,

49
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,160
