52
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:02,800
The Ancestral Court of the Human Race is gathering all its troops

53
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,130
to attack the Gu Family,

54
00:03:04,230 --> 00:03:06,100
with no time to care about the Imperial Pass.

55
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:08,660
This is a once-in-a-millennium opportunity for our Demon Clan.

56
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:09,360
Generals,

57
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,830
