58
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:13,690
and welcome my father's arrival.

59
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:15,930
Yes, General.

60
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:16,900
Over the years,

61
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:19,700
His Highness the Third Prince has been hiding in the Ancestral Court of the Human Race,

62
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,930
