64
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:26,020
It's time to make the human race pay in blood.

65
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:11,700
The Demon Clan is coming.

66
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,160
The Demon Clan is all over the mountains and plains.

67
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:13,930
Run.

68
00:04:14,230 --> 00:04:16,100
Luo Jinghong didn't guard the Imperial Pass properly.

69
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,899
