73
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:21,899
If the Imperial Pass is lost,

74
00:04:21,899 --> 00:04:23,930
Luo Jinghong will be the sinner of our human race forever.

75
00:04:23,930 --> 00:04:27,460
She can't atone for her sins even if she dies ten thousand times.

76
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:44,600
On the one hand, the Ancestral Court sends troops to attack the Gu family.

77
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:47,000
On the other hand, Luo Jinghong left her post without permission.

78
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,900
The Demon Clan invaded aggressively.

79
00:04:48,900 --> 00:04:49,460
Heaven

80
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:51,760
