90
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:20,390
and protect the destiny of the human race.

91
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,960
Protect our destiny!

92
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:22,760
Save the human race!

93
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:23,660
Protect our destiny!

94
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,600
Execute the false emperor!
